text: Anže Semenič (born 1 August 1993) is a Slovenian ski jumper. == Career == Semenič won the 2014–15 Continental Cup overall title. He made his World Cup debut in 2013. As part of the Slovenian team, he won his first World Cup competition in the team event in Planica in March 2015. He celebrated his first Grand Prix win at Nizhny Tagil in 2016.
